name: 40 CLOSE UP ARRIVALS AND DEPARTURES! Fall Plane Spotting at Calgary Airport
description:
November is usually one of the slower months here at YYC, but on a clear, calm day like this, you can still get some great traffic in some gorgeous afternoon light.

Please enjoy these 40 arrivals and departures on runway 17R!
